<a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/check">Check</a> whether or not <code>MI</code> should be treated like a copy for the mappings.

Copy like instruction are special for mapping because they don&#39;t have actual register constraints. Moreover, they sometimes have register classes assigned and we can just use that instead of failing to provide a generic mapping.
